para_trans: GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: SASB 1124 / P.No. 09 / PRASS-1 (CASE. 14)
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Under the aforesaid order, Mr. Sudhir Jaya Shetty has been transferred from the post of Room Officer to that of Under Secretary.
Temporarily promoted to the post, his post-promotional posting will be in the General Administration Department.
2. Now under this order, Mr. Sudhir Jaya Shetty has been promoted to the post of Under Secretary.
The posts have been partially changed for administrative reasons and their revised postings are medical.
It is being done in the education and pharmaceuticals department.
3. The terms and conditions of promotion of the above-mentioned officers shall continue to be as specified in the order in question.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
